These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, indian
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, writer
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, surfing
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the indian is in an even position##4
3. the writer is the chinese##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Nationality      | chinese  | indian   |
| Job   | writer     | bartender   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| Hobby     | singing | fishing    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, red
House: ranch-style, victorian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, baseball
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, tram
1. the person who's sport is baseball is in an odd position##4
2. the ranch-style house is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person who likes red is on the right of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Color          | purple     | red |
| House   | victorian | ranch-style  |
| Sport           | baseball         | skiing     |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
House: colonial, victorian
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, swimming
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the colonial house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| House    | victorian     | colonial |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| Sport         | rugby         | swimming        |
| Hobby   | fishing         | magic-tricks    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, june
There 2 different types of food: strawberry, zucchini
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, jet-ski
City: edinburgh, berlin
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Birthday      | june     | august |
| Food          | zucchini   | strawberry  |
| Transport         | roller | jet-ski     |
| City   | edinburgh  | berlin         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-5::.
