The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, biathlon
2 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble
There 2 different types of food: cherry, corn
1. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person eating corn is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | milk       |
| Sport           | biathlon      | climbing     |
| Game   | scrabble       | monopoly   |
| Food           | corn          | cherry |

