.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, bellflower
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian
City: nizza, edinburgh
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, november
1. the person who's birthday is in november is in an even position##4
2. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who growsbellflower is the dutch##1
4. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Flower           | bellflower | balloon-flower    |
| Nationality   | dutch       | egyptian |
| City           | nizza         | edinburgh    |
| Birthday         | april    | november   |

